The target function minimizes all losses and penalizes additional power flows (2). The solution is obtained by carrying out one optimization for every hour, i.e. four 15-min time steps at a time. 2minY=∑t=1T∑i=1N(aSiGγSiGt+aGSiγGSit+(bSiG+cSiG)⋅SiGt+(bGSi+cGSi)⋅GSit+(GLt+GCt)⋅p)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
